OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening and tonight in the
OL,7,Fnorth, with some light rain or drizzle
OL,8,Ftowards windward coasts and hills. Dry
OL,9,Felsewhere with clear spells and
OL,10,Ffeeling a little warmer than the
OL,11,Fprevious night.
