OL,13,CTuesday:FLargely dry with sunny spells
OL,14,Ffor many, although there will be some
OL,15,Fshowery light rain at times across
OL,16,Fnorthern coasts. Feeling warm in the
OL,17,Fsunshine, especially in the south.
